Package: betterwallpaper
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libmpv2 | libmpv1,
         swaybg | swww | hyprpaper
Recommends: linux-wallpaperengine
Description: Modern animated wallpaper manager for Linux
 BetterWallpaper is a feature-rich wallpaper manager for Wayland
 compositors like Hyprland. It supports:
  - Static images (PNG, JPG, WebP)
  - Video wallpapers (MP4, WebM)
  - Wallpaper Engine scenes (via linux-wallpaperengine)
  - Steam Workshop integration
  - Transitions and effects
  - Per-monitor configuration
